She's known for wearing next to nothing and causing a scene on the red carpet, but Skolopad ditched her usual antics in favour of a more sophisticated look at the SAFTAs on Saturday. She posted on image of herself on the red carpet wearing a gold evening gown at the awards. It's a far cry from her usual style. Fans took to the comments section on her page and applauded her new look. "You are wearing something decent for a change and look beautiful," commented one person. She recently told TshisaLIVE that she was interested in going into gospel music but was told she wouldn't be able to clean up her look. Well, here's the answer to that, doubters!